{
  "stem": "1518.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And as soon-- as soon as I took off my earphones, walked away like into the hall, I heard a-- a shell.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We knew already whether it's going to land here, or it's going to cross.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We knew already.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "As soon as I heard that shell, I dropped my face down on the hall.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That shell went right through the radio.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "His head was cut off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The-- the end of the-- was-- everything was smashed to pieces.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Another, I don't know, 2 or 3 seconds maybe, it would have been me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Actually, I was lucky in the army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I wasn't touched.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Mind you, I was like shell-- shell shock, because they used to throw bombs and grenades.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They had cases of the grenades, they used to throw at us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it's like shrapnel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's devastating.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So a bomb fell not too far from me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I would say maybe the other side of the hall, like the earth and everything, you know, from-- from the-- I couldn't hear for a little while, but I was OK.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I got out of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Your division, approximately how many were left when-- when you finally met the Americans?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Do you remember?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My division was a-- division's got three, like, it's called a polk, battalions.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they used to-- they used to regroup every time we used to get killed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I couldn't tell you exactly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we used to regroup every-- we used to be in the front line, let's say for two, three months.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then they used to give us a couple of weeks off, like in the back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Most of them were training the recruits.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We used to stay, like, in-- in towns, like in small towns.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And just relax, just relax.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they were training new recruits at the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
